  "detailed_description": "Welcome to <strong>memorel!</strong><br><br>Memorel is a card matching game suitable for all ages.<br>Give it to your kids, give it to your parents, give it to your grandma (she is really lovely), they'll all love it💗<br><br>If you like a little bit of a mental challenge and are a sweet tooth for beauty you have come to the right place.<br>Come, sit down and have a <i>morel</i>🍑<br><br>Let yourself get taken on an adventure through your memory via minds of great artists 🖼<br>And don't worry; it's not the Louvre. You can touch anything you like.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 200 cards with hand-picked imagery<br></li><li>More than 40 levels waiting for you to unlock them<br></li><li>Operated with just the click of your mouse<br></li><li>An atmosphere that helps you think clearly</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to <strong>memorel!</strong><br><br>Memorel is a card matching game suitable for all ages.<br>Give it to your kids, give it to your parents, give it to your grandma (she is really lovely), they'll all love it💗<br><br>If you like a little bit of a mental challenge and are a sweet tooth for beauty you have come to the right place.<br>Come, sit down and have a <i>morel</i>🍑<br><br>Let yourself get taken on an adventure through your memory via minds of great artists 🖼<br>And don't worry; it's not the Louvre. You can touch anything you like.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 200 cards with hand-picked imagery<br></li><li>More than 40 levels waiting for you to unlock them<br></li><li>Operated with just the click of your mouse<br></li><li>An atmosphere that helps you think clearly</li></ul>",
